name: UFO Senshi Yohko Chan
overview: You play with a cute extraterrestrial soldier girl named Yohko-chan, through a top view city maze full of enemies, after descending of UFO ship, will have to defend the city at all costs using his gun and his power digging to hide and evade enemies such as monsters, gargoyle, evil Knights and robots and pick coins to earn points and save the city.
